snippet.title: The Book of Unwritten Tales - Music & Artwork Trailer
snippet.description: More @ http://www.unwritten-tales.com | Artworks and Music from the adventure game "The Book of Unwritten Tales". It's a humorous homage to the RPG and fantasy genre with numerous allusions to literature and games like "Lord of the Rings", "World of Warcraft" and "Discworld".
